{
  "stem": "16245.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 349.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, on the first occasion, I showed a photocopy of our Schutzpass to a-- to a Gestapo officer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he accepted it, with perhaps one question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why haven't got-- you got the original?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told him my father has it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He accepted it no worries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew the second time he wouldn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to hide then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the subsequent occasions if I was there, I had to get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew I wouldn't get away with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother wasn't there by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't really living there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was living wherever I could, you know, wherever you could grab yourself a shelter for the night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, look, towards the end, there must have been 20 people there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vaguely, vaguely-- relations, friends, that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, their scope was limited by then because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they were either no railway connections anymore or Allied bombings were probably effective.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or they had no rolling stock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know which.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only deportation from Budapest that took place was on foot by the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a concentration camp near Budapest that the Germans operated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They emptied their camp many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kistarcsa. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that camp became quite famous because-- it might have been towards June, 1944, when the Regent regained his authority, he gave out the order that no more deportation of Jews from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, you've got to remember, all the Jews by then from the country were gone, deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Eichmann, apparently in defiance of that order, filled up a trainload with Jews from this camp and sent them off to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And apparently, somebody tipped off the Regent.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
